《'''女子监狱'''》（{{lang-en|''Orange Is the New Black''}}）是一部[[美国|美国]][[喜劇|喜劇]][[劇集|劇集]]，根据{{link-en|派珀·克爾曼|Piper Kerman}}的监狱经历回忆录《{{link-en|Orange Is the New Black: My Year in a Women's Prison|Orange Is the New Black: My Year in a Women's Prison}}》改编，制作人为{{link-en|珍姬·可汗|Jenji Kohan}}，由{{Link-en|獅門電視|Lionsgate Television}}和Tilted Productions聯合製作。2013年7月11日在[[Netflix|Netflix]]首播。<ref name="premiere">{{cite web|url = http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/netflix-orange-new-black-premiere-date-jenji-kohan-448610|title = Netflix Sets Premiere Date for Jenji Kohan's 'Orange Is the New Black'|work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|last = Goldberg|first = Lesley|date = 2013-04-30|accessdate = 2013-04-30|archive-date = 2016-03-03|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204253/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/netflix-orange-new-black-premiere-date-jenji-kohan-448610|dead-url = no}}</ref>
<ref name="based">{{cite web | url = http://www.deadline.com/2011/07/netflix-eyeing-second-original-series-comedy-from-weeds-creator-jenji-kohan/#more-149314 | title = Netflix Eyeing Second Original Series – Comedy From ''Weeds'' Creator Jenji Kohan | accessdate = 2013-12-13 | archive-date = 2013-10-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131019100036/http://www.deadline.com/2011/07/netflix-eyeing-second-original-series-comedy-from-weeds-creator-jenji-kohan/#more-149314 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="duocast">{{cite web|url = http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/duo-cast-in-netflixs-orange-is-the-new-black-don-stark-upped-on-vhs-bounce/|title = Duo Cast In Netflix's 'Orange Is The New Black', Don Stark Upped On VH's 'Bounce'|last = Andreeva|first = Nellie|date = 2012-09-17|publisher = Deadline.com|accessdate = 2012-09-17|archive-date = 2013-10-19|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131019084632/http://www.deadline.com/2012/09/duo-cast-in-netflixs-orange-is-the-new-black-don-stark-upped-on-vhs-bounce/|dead-url = no}}</ref>2018年10月，確定第七季會是最後一季，於2019年7月26日播放。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.vulture.com/2018/10/orange-is-the-new-black-end-season-7.html |title = Orange Is the New Black's Prison Sentence Will End With Season 7 |author = Dee Lockett |publisher = Vulture |language = en}}</ref>

本劇因對[[囚犯|囚犯]]極具人性化的描寫以及包含[[種族|種族]]、[[性別|性別]]、[[性取向|性取向]]及[[政治|政治]]等多元議題而備受讚譽。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/how-orange-is-the-new-black-humanizes-inmates/2013/07/26/d1559bac-f3e5-11e2-9434-60440856fadf_story.html |title=How 'Orange Is the New Black' humanizes inmates |website=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] |first=Seth |last=Abramson |date=July 26, 2013 |access-date=September 2, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bustle.com/articles/28263-has-orange-is-the-new-black-changed-the-way-we-think-of-prisoners-former-inmates-say |title=Has 'Orange is the New Black' Changed the Way We Think of Prisoners? Former Inmates Say No, But There's Progress Ahead |website=[[Bustle_(magazine)|Bustle]] |first=Rachel |last=Simon |date=June 17, 2014 |access-date=September 2, 2015}}</ref><ref name="Great Orange grantland">{{cite web |url=http://grantland.com/hollywood-prospectus/the-great-orange-is-the-new-black-is-suddenly-the-best-netflix-binge-watch-series-yet/ |title=The Great Orange Is the New Black Is Suddenly the Best Netflix Series Yet |website=[[Grantland|Grantland]] |first=Andy |last=Greenwald |date=July 15, 2013 |access-date=September 1, 2015}}</ref><ref name="NYPost ignites">{{cite web |url=https://nypost.com/2014/06/04/orange-is-the-new-black-ignites-a-tv-revolution-for-women/ [title='Orange[ Is the New Black' ignites a TV revolution for women |website=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]] |first=Robert |last=Rorke |date=June 4, 2014 |access-date=September 2, 2015}}</ref>劇集中又展示了[[美國監獄|美國監獄]]各種形式的腐敗，包括監獄[[私有化|私有化]]、私營監獄削減資金以賺取數百萬美元的利潤、人滿為患、[[獄警|獄警]]的虐待行為和[[種族歧視|種族歧視]]等（以及其他問題）如何影響著囚犯和獄警的安全、健康和福利；以及監獄無法履行其作為懲戒機關的基本[[法律責任|法律責任]]和[[道德義務|道德義務]]。<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Terry|first=April|date=July 2016|title=Surveying Issues That Arise in Women's Prisons: A Content Critique of Orange Is the New Black: OITNB: Women's Prisons|journal=Sociology Compass|volume=10|issue=7|pages=553–566|doi=10.1111/soc4.12388}}</ref>

自播出以來，此劇獲得了16項[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]提名和四個獎項。在第一季中，獲得了12項艾美獎提名，最後贏得最佳喜劇、最佳喜劇寫作和最佳導演等三項大獎。<ref name="Emmy">{{cite web |url=http://www.emmys.com/shows/orange-new-black |title=Orange Is The New Black |publisher=Television Academy |access-date=April 14, 2016}}</ref>主演[[泰勒·席林|泰勒·席林]]獲得[[金球獎劇情類劇集最佳女主角|金球獎劇情類劇集最佳女主角]]提名。<ref name="GG">{{cite web |url=http://www.hfpa.org/browse/?param=/film/26477 |title=Orange is the New Black |publisher=[[Hollywood_Foreign_Press_Association|Hollywood Foreign Press Association]] |access-date=June 11, 2015}}</ref>在第二季中，本劇又獲得了四個[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]提名，其中包括最佳戲劇；飾演瘋眼的女演員[[烏佐·阿杜巴|烏佐·阿杜巴]]贏得了戲劇最佳女配角。《勁》是第一部在喜劇和戲劇類影片中同時獲艾美獎提名的劇集。<ref name="Birnbaum">{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2015/tv/news/jenji-kohan-orange-is-the-new-black-showrunner-1201555759/ |title='Orange Is the New Black' Boss Jenji Kohan on Running the Show Her Way |website=Variety |first=Debra |last=Birnbaum |date=August 4, 2015 |access-date=September 1, 2015}}</ref>另外還獲得了六項[[金球獎|金球獎]]提名，六項[[美國編劇工會獎|美國編劇工會獎]]獎提名；以及[[美國製片人協會|美國製片人協會]]、[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]和[[皮博迪獎|皮博迪獎]]分別一項獎狀提名。

2013年，美國電影學院將本劇評為年度十大電視節目之一。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/afiawards/AFIAwards13.aspx |title=AFI Awards 2013 |publisher=American Film Institute |access-date=April 16, 2016}}</ref>2019年，獲《[[衛報|衛報]]》評選為21世紀百大最佳電視節目之一。<ref>{{cite web |title=The 100 best TV shows of the 21st century |url=https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2019/sep/16/100-best-tv-shows-of-the-21st-century |website=The Guardian |date=September 13, 2019 |access-date=September 23, 2019}}</ref>

==劇情==
故事圍繞一名年約30多歲的女子派珀·查普曼（[[泰勒·席林|泰勒·席林]]飾）展開，她開始在[[紐約州|紐約州]]北部的低戒備女子[[美國監禁制度|聯邦監獄]]—利奇菲爾德監獄服刑。查普曼本來正在紐約過著守秩序又安穩的生活，但因在多年前協助毒品走私犯兼前女友艾莉克斯·沃斯（[[劳拉·普莱潘|劳拉·普莱潘]]飾）運毒，在某日突然被起訴過去的罪行繼而入獄，結果破壞了她與未婚夫、家人和朋友的關係。在監獄中，查普曼與使其入獄的艾莉克斯重遇，期間重新審視兩人關係。與此同時，查普曼和其他囚犯需面對監獄裡的眾多鬥爭和不公義。
