==制作==
節目創作人珍姬·可汗閱讀過朋友寄給她的派珀·克爾曼的監獄回憶錄後，聯絡克爾曼舉行了一次會議向其介紹電視劇改編。可汗指出，她大部分時間都在向克爾曼詢問其在書中描述的經歷而不是一味推銷，這讓克爾曼覺得很吸引。可汗讓她知道她是這本書的粉絲，克爾曼同意改編並簽字。<ref name="Collidermay">{{cite web |last1=Radish |first1=Christina |title=Creator Jenji Kohan Talks ORANGE IS THE NEW BLACK, Her Research Into Prison Life, and Graphic Sex Scenes |url=https://collider.com/jenji-kohan-orange-is-the-new-black-interview/ |website=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]] |date=July 7, 2013 |access-date=May 3, 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title='Orange' Creator Jenji Kohan: 'Piper Was My Trojan Horse' |url=https://www.npr.org/2013/08/13/211639989/orange-creator-jenji-kohan-piper-was-my-trojan-horse |publisher=NPR |date=August 13, 2013 |access-date=May 3, 2016}}</ref>2011年7月，據透露[[Netflix|Netflix]]正在與獅門電視協議將派珀·克爾曼的監獄回憶錄改編為13集電視節目，並由可汗擔任製作人。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.deadline.com/2011/07/netflix-eyeing-second-original-series-comedy-from-weeds-creator-jenji-kohan/ |title=Netflix Eyeing Second Original Series – Comedy From ''Weeds'' Creator Jenji Kohan |website=Deadline Hollywood |first=Nellie |last=Andreeva |date=July 22, 2011 |access-date=May 2, 2016}}</ref>2011年11月，協議通過，電視劇改編獲批准。<ref>{{cite web |last=Andreeva |first=Nellie |url=https://www.deadline.com/2011/11/netflix-lionsgate-tv-closing-deal-for-jenji-kohans-orange-is-the-new-black-comedy/ |title=Netflix, Lionsgate TV Closing Deal For Jenji Kohan's 'Orange Is The New Black' Comedy |website=Deadline Hollywood |date=November 11, 2011 |access-date=May 2, 2016}}</ref>可汗最初想讓[[姬蒂·荷姆絲|姬蒂·荷姆絲]]扮演派珀·查普曼的角色並會見了女演員討論此事，但其因忙於其他工作行程所以推辭。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nypost.com/2014/08/06/katie-holmes-almost-starred-in-orange-is-the-new-black/|title=Katie Holmes almost starred in 'Orange is the New Black'|website=[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]|date=August 6, 2014|access-date=August 16, 2018}}</ref>演員陣容於2012年8月公開，首先宣佈由[[泰勒·席林|泰勒·席林]]飾演派珀·查普曼，並由[[傑森·畢格斯|傑森·畢格斯]]飾演派珀的未婚夫賴瑞·布魯姆。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/jason-biggs-netflix-orange-new-black-jenji-kohan-weeds-369610 |title=Jason Biggs to Co-Star in Netflix's 'Orange Is the New Black' (Exclusive) |last=Goldberg |first=Lesley |date=September 12, 2012 |website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |access-date=September 12, 2012}}</ref>

《勁》設置為位於紐約州利奇菲爾德的一個虛構的低戒備監獄中，利奇菲爾德是紐約州北部的一個真正存在的城鎮，但那裡其實沒有聯邦監獄。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://brooklyn.news12.com/news/hudson-buzz-1.3774483/netflix-series-orange-is-the-new-black-filming-in-rockland-1.4761288|title=Netflix series 'Orange is the New Black' filming in Rockland|last=Serico|first=Chris|date=March 7, 2013|website=Newsday|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014171403/http://brooklyn.news12.com/news/hudson-buzz-1.3774483/netflix-series-orange-is-the-new-black-filming-in-rockland-1.4761288|archive-date=October 14, 2013|access-date=March 28, 2013}}</ref>本劇於2013年3月7日開始在[[羅克蘭縣|羅克蘭縣]]的前羅克蘭兒童精神病學中心拍攝，該建築是當時的羅克蘭州立醫院（Rockland State Hospital）的一部分，建於1970年，直到2010年關閉。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Pate |first1=Caroline |title='Orange is the New Black' Title Sequence Uses Actual Former Prisoners |url=http://www.bustle.com/articles/3924-orange-is-the-new-black-title-sequence-uses-actual-former-prisoners |website=Bustle |date=August 21, 2013 |access-date=May 3, 2016}}</ref>

